				<div class="comment-author vcard">
			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/19f0559f5c683fefdadf42b47bd6c74c?s=32&#038;d=retro&#038;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' />			<cite class="fn"><a href='http://bathyderm.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Aggie</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>
		
		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://chriscondello.wordpress.com/2014/03/16/a-plant-a-day-till-spring-day-87-tomato/comment-page-1/#comment-3135">
			March 18, 2014 at 6:42 pm</a>		</div>

		<p> <span class='wp-smiley emoji emoji-smile' title=':)'>:)</span> I asked for top PRODUCERS and you gave me top FLAVOR. Makes me laugh. I ordered all heirloom seeds for the garden we will sell from, and I&#8217;m hoping we&#8217;ll have enough to sell. <span class='wp-smiley emoji emoji-wink' title=';)'>;)</span> &#8230; Thanks.</p>

		<div class="reply">
					</div>
				</div>
		</li><!-- #comment-## -->
		<li class="comment byuser comment-author-delo024 bypostauthor even depth-3 parent highlander-comment" id="comment-3137">
				<div id="div-comment-3137" class="comment-body">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
			<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/c0530e18a26d2db5ba1733c22fbc04b7?s=32&#038;d=retro&#038;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' />			<cite class="fn"><a href='http://chriscondello.wordpress.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>C.Condello</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>
		
		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://chriscondello.wordpress.com/2014/03/16/a-plant-a-day-till-spring-day-87-tomato/comment-page-1/#comment-3137">
			March 19, 2014 at 4:49 am</a>		</div>

		<p>I think my top producer would have to be Mortgage Lifter&#8230; Or Hillbilly Flame&#8230; I forgot you are on a working farm&#8230; Let me think about this for a day or two&#8230; I may reach out to a friend as well&#8230;</p>
<p>Out of curiosity&#8230; What did you order?</p>

		<div class="reply">
					</div>
				</div>
		</li><!-- #comment-## -->
		<li class="comment byuser comment-author-aedoue odd alt depth-3 highlander-comment" id="comment-3144">
				<div id="div-comment-3144" class="comment-body">
				<div class="comment-author vcard">
			<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/19f0559f5c683fefdadf42b47bd6c74c?s=32&#038;d=retro&#038;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' />			<cite class="fn"><a href='http://bathyderm.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Aggie</a></cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>
		
