		<p>Thanks, Chris! We got Mortgage Lifter, Black Krim, Brandywine, Cherokee Purple, Eva Purple Ball, Paul Robeson, Isis Candy Cherry, Italian Heirloom, Nyagous, Speckled Roman, Gypsy, and Carbon. The soil was grass until last fall, so we have our fingers crossed: XX.</p>

